        <trans-unit id="103" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>This example shows how to use the              <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DoubleAnimationUsingPath&gt;</ph> class to move an object along a path defined by a              <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.PathGeometry&gt;</ph>.</source>
